 engaging library instruction, both in an online environment and in personStrong project management and organizational skillsDemonstrated initiative, creativity, and problem-solving skillsAcademic credentials or work experience in the sciences an assetThis position is .75 and expected to work roughly a 22.5-hour week. Salary is based on the Langara Faculty Association pay scale and has a range of $$4,360-$6,990 monthly. Posted salary is pro-rated based on hours of work. Placement on the scale is a set calculation based on previous experience. More information can be found in the LFA Collective Agreement.Submit your application online: Employment Opportunities (myworkdayjobs.com) Compensation $4,360 - $6,990 Monthly. Placement on the scale is a set calculation based on previous experience Closes: 9 July, 2023 Langara College Vancouver , BC Policies and Terms of Use · jobboard@bcla.bc.ca / BCLA PO BOX 19008, Rocky Point PO, Port Moody, BC V3H 0J1 window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
